<h1>ShotCaller</h1>

<p>Predict the results of the 2026 World Cup matches and compete on the leaderboard.</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Matches</strong> – see all matches and results</li>
    <li><strong>Predict</strong> – enter your name and predict scores before kickoff</li>
    <li><strong>Leaderboard</strong> – see who's winning</li>
</ul>

<p>Scoring: 3 points for the exact result, 1 point for the correct outcome, 0 otherwise.</p>